item.title: Rebecca Black vs. STAR WARS
item.dc:creator: Israel Curtis
item.description: The Star Wars crew spoofs Rebecca Black 'Friday' in their own version, called 'Primeday'. Yes, Primeday is actually one of the days of the week in the Star Wars universe. SOMAKAT provided the music arrangement, vocals (featuring Lauralyn Curtis), and mix.

item.title: The Star Wars That I Used To Know
item.dc:creator: Israel Curtis
item.description: The geniuses at TeddieFilms spoof of Gotye's "Somebody That I Used To Know", done Star Wars style, of course. It's a story of heartbreak to which Star Wars fans everywhere can relate. And even with all that heart ache, it's still a better love story than Twilight. Somakat provided the music arrangement, vocals, and mix.
